		<td><b>Re: Two Controllers for one Player</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />IIRC, Smash TV has a both-controllers-for-one-player mode. Basically emulating a single dual-stick controller using both D pads.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
